<h1 class="entry-title">The Curious Reemergence of Little Platoons</h1>
<div class="entry-author">
			written by <a href="https://quillette.com/author/alexandra-hudson/" title="All posts by Alexandra Hudson">Alexandra Hudson</a> </div><!-- end .entry-author -->
</header><!-- end .entry-header -->
<div class="entry-thumbnail">
<a href="https://quillette.com/2018/10/04/the-curious-reemergence-of-little-platoons/" title="Permalink to The Curious Reemergence of Little Platoons"><img alt="" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" data-lazy-src="https://d24fkeqntp1r7r.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04055144/AdobeStock_158924448-e1538632439387.jpeg" height="800" src="https://quillette.com/wp-content/plugins/jetpack/modules/lazy-images/images/1x1.trans.gif" width="1200"/></a>
