						October 6, 2018</a>
</li>
</ul><!-- end .comment-meta -->
</div><!-- end .comment-details -->
<div class="comment-text">
<p>@fairleft</p>
<p>Maybe “independents” are left out because they have less of a need to be included in these group sessions. When dealing with hyper partisan or hyper political people, I’ve noticed that you don’t really need the skills of logic or rhetoric. What you need instead are the skills of a cult deprogrammer.</p>
</div><!-- end .comment-text -->
<div class="comment-reply"><a aria-label="Reply to Circuses and Bread" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-38976" onclick='return addComment.moveForm( "comment-38976", "38976", "respond", "84625" )' rel="nofollow">Reply</a></div>
